[SPEAKER_00] Ono, sedam, osam puta,

1246
00:39:24,619 --> 00:39:25,980
[SPEAKER_00] idem ja to vidim šta je to,

1247
00:39:25,980 --> 00:39:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] šta se tamo događa,

1248
00:39:26,980 --> 00:39:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] kakva je to ljubav.

1249
00:39:28,019 --> 00:39:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] Petar njega pita,

1250
00:39:30,219 --> 00:39:32,179
[SPEAKER_00] Isus njega pita,

1251
00:39:32,179 --> 00:39:33,719
[SPEAKER_00] Petre,

1252
00:39:33,719 --> 00:39:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] jel ti mene agapiraš?

1253
00:39:36,139 --> 00:39:37,780
[SPEAKER_00] Grečka riječ, agape.

1254
00:39:37,780 --> 00:39:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] Agape znači ona ljubav

1255
00:39:40,300 --> 00:39:41,860
[SPEAKER_00] gdje daješ sve do boli

1256
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] i ne tražiš ništa na trak.

1257
00:39:43,179 --> 00:39:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] To znači žrtva,

1258
00:39:44,699 --> 00:39:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] služenje, služenje, služenje.

1259
00:39:46,579 --> 00:39:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] I Petar odgovara,

1260
00:39:47,659 --> 00:39:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] pa ja te filiram,

1261
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:50,239
[SPEAKER_00] volim te kao prijatelj.

1262
00:39:50,239 --> 00:39:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1263
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] jel ti Petre mene tako ljubiš

1264
00:39:54,579 --> 00:39:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] da si spreman da život za mene

1265
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] bez uvjeta,

1266
00:39:58,199 --> 00:39:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] bez kriterija.

1267
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, pa, okej si.

1268
00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Petar odgovara,

1269
00:40:04,239 --> 00:40:05,360
[SPEAKER_00] filija, ok?

1270
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] To je kao prijateljska ljubav.

1271
00:40:06,820 --> 00:40:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] To ti je ljubav koja je uvjetovana.

1272
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo prijatelji

1273
00:40:11,460 --> 00:40:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer igramo nogomet petak večer.

1274
00:40:13,159 --> 00:40:14,760
[SPEAKER_00] To su moji nogometni prijatelji.

1275
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] Onda imam moji prijatelji

1276
00:40:16,579 --> 00:40:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] s kimi idem pet sanje.

1277
00:40:17,539 --> 00:40:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] Onda imam kvartovske prijatelji.

1278
00:40:18,960 --> 00:40:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je uvjetovano prijateljstvo, jel?

1279
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] Što nije loše.

1280
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Isus ga pita,

1281
00:40:24,260 --> 00:40:26,239
[SPEAKER_00] Petre, a ti mene agapiraš?

1282
00:40:26,239 --> 00:40:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

1283
00:40:27,159 --> 00:40:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] volim te ko prijatelja.

1284
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] I pita ga drugi puta.

1285
00:40:30,300 --> 00:40:33,260
[SPEAKER_00] Petre, a ti mene agapiraš?

1286
00:40:33,260 --> 00:40:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže, pa,

1287
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] volim te ko prijatelja.

1288
00:40:35,900 --> 00:40:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] Sad parafriziram prebod, jel?

1289
00:40:38,619 --> 00:40:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] I treći put.

1290
00:40:39,559 --> 00:40:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže,

1291
00:40:40,739 --> 00:40:41,440
[SPEAKER_00] okej, skužim.

1292
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] Petre, a ti mene voliš ko prijatelja?

1293
00:40:44,699 --> 00:40:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] Onda Petar kaže,

1294
00:40:45,820 --> 00:40:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] pa Isus, pa rekao sam ti već

1295
00:40:47,139 --> 00:40:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] da volim te ko prijatelja.

1296
00:40:48,159 --> 00:40:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Isus čak spušta kriterij.

1297
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1298
00:40:53,619 --> 00:40:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nije spreman.

1299
00:40:54,539 --> 00:40:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nije spreman.

1300
00:40:56,559 --> 00:40:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je fascinantno,

1301
00:40:58,500 --> 00:40:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] Evanđelje.

1302
00:40:59,139 --> 00:41:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači što ovo znači?

1303
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:03,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da gospodin tebe uzme

1304
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,679
[SPEAKER_00] onako u toj fazi,

1305
00:41:04,679 --> 00:41:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] nisu svi spremni na sve.

1306
00:41:07,519 --> 00:41:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1307
00:41:10,619 --> 00:41:12,260
[SPEAKER_00] neki dan je bila jedna djevojka,

1308
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:14,739
[SPEAKER_00] ona je se isto nedavno obratila,

1309
00:41:14,739 --> 00:41:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] i sad ona nju muči

1310
00:41:16,539 --> 00:41:19,360
[SPEAKER_00] što ona na faksu

1311
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] nije uspjela

1312
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] obraćati ljudi

1313
00:41:22,099 --> 00:41:22,820
[SPEAKER_00] i opomenjati.

1314
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:24,300
[SPEAKER_00] Lako, polako, draga.

1315
00:41:24,300 --> 00:41:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ti nisi pozvana na to.

1316
00:41:26,039 --> 00:41:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] Polako.

1317
00:41:27,679 --> 00:41:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nije despot.

1318
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] I obraćenici moji veliki problem s time.

1319
00:41:33,059 --> 00:41:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite šta Isus ovdje radi.

1320
00:41:35,340 --> 00:41:36,820
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju, kada on vidi

1321
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:37,440
[SPEAKER_00] da ne može,

1322
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:38,639
[SPEAKER_00] ne zna šta je Agape,

1323
00:41:38,639 --> 00:41:40,099
[SPEAKER_00] on kaže, dobro, Petre,

1324
00:41:40,099 --> 00:41:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] ili me voliš ko prijatelja?

1325
00:41:41,400 --> 00:41:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, pa naravno da te volim.

1326
00:41:42,800 --> 00:41:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro, najde.

1327
00:41:44,699 --> 00:41:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ona mu kaže,

1328
00:41:45,619 --> 00:41:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] ali jednog dana,

1329
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] Petre,

1330
00:41:47,519 --> 00:41:49,739
[SPEAKER_00] ićeš kamo ti ne želiš ići.

1331
00:41:49,739 --> 00:41:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] To je Agape.

1332
00:41:50,739 --> 00:41:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nisi još spreman na to.

1333
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ok?

1334
00:41:54,579 --> 00:41:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu faleluja za ovo evanđelje.

1335
00:41:57,239 --> 00:42:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jer većina nismo spremni.

1336
00:42:01,119 --> 00:42:04,860
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite kako ta duhovna zrelost je važna.

1337
00:42:04,860 --> 00:42:06,780
[SPEAKER_00] Priznati svoje ograničenje.

1338
00:42:06,780 --> 00:42:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] Petar je već se zaletio,

1339
00:42:09,519 --> 00:42:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] daću život za tebe.

1340
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, right.

1341
00:42:11,039 --> 00:42:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] Daj, Petre, smiri sa čemu.

1342
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] Maj, šuti, šuti.

1343
00:42:14,659 --> 00:42:16,059
[SPEAKER_00] ali,

1344
00:42:16,059 --> 00:42:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] ipak Petar ima to srce.

1345
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] Daćeš ti jednog dana.

1346
00:42:19,420 --> 00:42:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ne još, Petre.

1347
00:42:20,079 --> 00:42:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] Sam polako.

1348
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1349
00:42:21,980 --> 00:42:23,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1350
00:42:25,579 --> 00:42:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] I sada, treća faza, ta zadnja,

1351
00:42:30,099 --> 00:42:32,139
[SPEAKER_00] duhovna zrelost.

1352
00:42:32,139 --> 00:42:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da su mnogi u toj fazi.

1353
00:42:35,199 --> 00:42:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja mislim da paralelno mnogi se čistimo.

1354
00:42:38,900 --> 00:42:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, što želim reći, ovo nije ono baš kronološki, strogo.

1355
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ja se čistim još uvijek, ali mogu se prepoznati i u drugoj fazi.

1356
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako zvijek, a to je tako zvijek, a to je tako zvona faza sjedinjenje, a to je nakon silska duha svijetoga, gdje je taj isti Petar, koji je bio tako pun straha, koji je jedna slušknja, kad je rekla bu, on je skočio.

1357
00:42:59,719 --> 00:43:06,139
[SPEAKER_00] Sada, u sili i u snazi, navješta u jeruzalinskim ulicama i tri tišće ljudi se obraćaju.

1358
00:43:06,139 --> 00:43:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dovode ga tamo i bićuju ga i on kaže, raduj se Ivane, što možemo trpiti radi imena.

1359
00:43:13,460 --> 00:43:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] Eto.

1360
00:43:15,099 --> 00:43:18,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ali šta se sad događa kod Petra?

1361
00:43:18,340 --> 00:43:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] Prije Petar je bio malo sebićan, pa je tražio svoje, pa nemoj ti na križić, pa ovo, pa ona, pa se malo boji.

1362
00:43:25,400 --> 00:43:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sada, duhovno očinstvo, sada Petar širi vjeru, sada Petar dovede drugi ljudi do Isusa Hrista.

1363
00:43:33,920 --> 00:43:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] To je pravo krišćanstvo, to je duhovna zrelost.

1364
00:43:36,260 --> 00:43:47,320
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, prvo se malo on čisti, on nam dođe do jednog ekvilibrija, a on dan prijeđe na evangelizaciju, odnosno dovođenje druge Isusu Hrista.

1365
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:52,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti nemaš potrebu govoriti o Isu, još ga nisi upoznao.

1366
00:43:53,480 --> 00:43:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nemaš potrebu govoriti o Isu, ako imaš potrebu govoriti, to još nije dovoljno da govoriš o Njemu.

1367
00:43:58,619 --> 00:44:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nima neki ljudi koji ne smiju govoriti o Njemu. Ne još. Ne još.

1368
00:44:02,260 --> 00:44:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Bogu hvala ako imaš potrebu.

1369
00:44:05,920 --> 00:44:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] Petar je došao u jednu fazu gdje ne samo da govori o Hristu, nego on trpi radi Isusa.

1370
00:44:13,300 --> 00:44:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] On trpi radi Isusa i čini čudesa i tako dalje.

1371
00:44:18,360 --> 00:44:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] To je ta faza dijela apostolski, mi to možemo vidjeti.

1372
00:44:21,880 --> 00:44:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] I ta njegova hrabrost i tako dalje.

1373
00:44:24,920 --> 00:44:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] Engleski se kaže boldness.

1374
00:44:27,500 --> 00:44:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] On navješta u sili i u snazi.

1375
00:44:36,519 --> 00:44:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, na kraju, suma sumarum.

1376
00:44:38,480 --> 00:44:49,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kajanje, stjecanje, znanje, poniznost.

1377
00:44:54,280 --> 00:45:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon pada dizanje, ja mogu samo misliti kako je bilo Petru kad je zatajio Isusa.

1378
00:45:00,719 --> 00:45:01,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako teško.

1379
00:45:01,699 --> 00:45:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što vidim kod mnogih ljudi.

1380
00:45:03,559 --> 00:45:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dožive poraz.

1381
00:45:05,460 --> 00:45:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] Padnu u težak grijeh.

1382
00:45:07,840 --> 00:45:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi svećenici mi dolaze na ispovjed.

1383
00:45:11,420 --> 00:45:15,460
[SPEAKER_00] I on taj svećenik isti koji padne u težak nekih grijeh.

1384
00:45:15,460 --> 00:45:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tako on...

1385
00:45:17,559 --> 00:45:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] Pazi u koju džavosku zamku on pada.

1386
00:45:19,380 --> 00:45:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] Sad on kaže, e nisam dostojan sad govoriti jer sam ja dvoličnik jer sam ja pa...

1387
00:45:25,059 --> 00:45:25,340
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ću...

1388
00:45:25,340 --> 00:45:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne budalo, šuti.

1389
00:45:26,519 --> 00:45:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ti moraš govoriti zato što ti nisi garantor ove istine.

1390
00:45:31,039 --> 00:45:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ti jesi dvoličnik ukoliko ne živiš ono što propovjedaš.

1391
00:45:34,719 --> 00:45:38,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ali prijatelju dragi, ti si pozvan na vještati i dizati se.

1392
00:45:38,320 --> 00:45:40,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jer šta džavao radi nakon pada?

1393
00:45:40,480 --> 00:45:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] Skačeti na glavu i kao vi šta si napravio.

1394
00:45:42,579 --> 00:45:44,039
[SPEAKER_00] A šta radi prije pada?

1395
00:45:44,039 --> 00:45:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] Padni, padni, griješi, griješi.

1396
00:45:46,039 --> 00:45:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] A nakon pada, eto vidi šta si napravio.

1397
00:45:48,699 --> 00:45:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] Krivnja nakon ispovjedne dolazi od Boga.

1398
00:45:50,659 --> 00:45:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ja vidim kod obračenike i kod nas kršćana, mladi katolici,

1399
00:45:56,559 --> 00:45:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] to da žare, žare, žare.

1400
00:45:59,599 --> 00:46:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] I onda padnu i onda ništa.

1401
00:46:01,980 --> 00:46:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] Nema ga više nigdje.

1402
00:46:02,840 --> 00:46:05,820
[SPEAKER_00] I još jedan savjet, molim vas.

1403
00:46:05,820 --> 00:46:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam skruvao jedan termin, a to su posvuduše.

1404
00:46:11,679 --> 00:46:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta su posvuduše?

1405
00:46:13,039 --> 00:46:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vidim da neki znaju.

1406
00:46:15,539 --> 00:46:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] To znači ponedljak večer sam u Skacu,

1407
00:46:19,460 --> 00:46:22,179
[SPEAKER_00] a utorak večer sam kod, ne znam,

1408
00:46:22,179 --> 00:46:24,320
[SPEAKER_00] na novo sredu sam kod Don Damira,

1409
00:46:24,320 --> 00:46:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] četvrtak sam i tako dalje.

1410
00:46:26,599 --> 00:46:27,139
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte.

1411
00:46:27,139 --> 00:46:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je dobro, ima vrijeme i za to.

1412
00:46:30,039 --> 00:46:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] Malo duhovni šoping.

1413
00:46:33,420 --> 00:46:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je.

1414
00:46:34,099 --> 00:46:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali znate šta je znak duhovne zrelosti?

1415
00:46:38,019 --> 00:46:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] Posvećenje.

1416
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] Posvećenje negdje.

1417
00:46:42,599 --> 00:46:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta je meni najgore?

1418
00:46:45,760 --> 00:46:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] Kada meni neko dođe i pita me za savjet.

1419
00:46:48,320 --> 00:46:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] Momak, djevojka.

1420
00:46:50,659 --> 00:46:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Ramos mi je rekao,

1421
00:46:52,880 --> 00:46:53,780
[SPEAKER_00] znači šta, izađe.

1422
00:46:53,780 --> 00:46:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] Izađe.

1423
00:46:55,440 --> 00:46:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, šta ta osoba radi?

1424
00:46:57,840 --> 00:47:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ide kod Ramosa

1425
00:47:01,380 --> 00:47:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] i pokupi ono što želi.

1426
00:47:03,440 --> 00:47:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ide ondan, dođe kod Don Damira,

1427
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] pokupi ono što želi.

1428
00:47:08,579 --> 00:47:11,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ondan će možda ići,

1429
00:47:11,099 --> 00:47:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] evo, Paterike odšla,

1430
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:13,260
[SPEAKER_00] ode malo kod Paterike,

1431
00:47:13,260 --> 00:47:14,739
[SPEAKER_00] pokupiš,

1432
00:47:14,739 --> 00:47:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] onda ide kod ovoga fratra na Kapitolu

1433
00:47:17,119 --> 00:47:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

1434
00:47:17,840 --> 00:47:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako nezrelo.

1435
00:47:20,159 --> 00:47:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kako je to nezrelo?

1436
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:24,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kad skužim da se to događa,

1437
00:47:24,219 --> 00:47:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] ja odmah prekidam razgor,

1438
00:47:25,659 --> 00:47:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] izađi iz Mugurga.

1439
00:47:26,460 --> 00:47:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ne moraš izaći iz Mugurga,

1440
00:47:28,420 --> 00:47:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali nećemo pričati više o ovom,

1441
00:47:29,440 --> 00:47:31,280
[SPEAKER_00] možemo pričati o sportu,

1442
00:47:31,380 --> 00:47:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] politici, o izborima i tako dalje.

1443
00:47:32,880 --> 00:47:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ali nećemo ovo.

1444
00:47:34,079 --> 00:47:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] To je duhovno nezrelo.

1445
00:47:36,579 --> 00:47:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] Zato dobro je naći duhovnika

1446
00:47:38,980 --> 00:47:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] i drža se njega.

1447
00:47:39,900 --> 00:47:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] A mijenjanje ispovjednika?

1448
00:47:41,980 --> 00:47:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] Mijenjanje ispovjednika?

1449
00:47:50,579 --> 00:47:53,079
[SPEAKER_00] Nemu ja nemu sve reći.

1450
00:47:53,079 --> 00:47:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja njemu ovo reći.

1451
00:47:56,380 --> 00:47:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ići kod onoga i tako dalje.

1452
00:47:59,179 --> 00:48:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste čuli za onoga lika?

1453
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] Četardeset godina se nije ispovjedio.

1454
00:48:04,079 --> 00:48:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ono varo ženu,

1455
00:48:05,260 --> 00:48:06,619
[SPEAKER_00] nagovoro ženu na pobačaj.

1456
00:48:06,619 --> 00:48:08,800
[SPEAKER_00] Krao od radnike,

1457
00:48:08,800 --> 00:48:09,659
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ono,

1458
00:48:09,659 --> 00:48:11,280
[SPEAKER_00] došao kod svećenika,

1459
00:48:11,280 --> 00:48:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] ispovjedio se.

1460
00:48:11,960 --> 00:48:13,340
[SPEAKER_00] I ono svećenika je kao,

1461
00:48:13,340 --> 00:48:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu, hvala četardeset godina.

1462
00:48:14,360 --> 00:48:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je pokora.

1463
00:48:15,300 --> 00:48:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, ok, priznaj sve ženi.

1464
00:48:17,619 --> 00:48:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] I pokora mu je bilo,

1465
00:48:18,599 --> 00:48:20,639
[SPEAKER_00] ajme, meni, vrati novce koliko je moguće.

1466
00:48:20,639 --> 00:48:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, skoro nemoguće,

1467
00:48:22,219 --> 00:48:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali mora napraviti reparaciju za to.

1468
00:48:24,380 --> 00:48:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] I ovaj izlađe iz ispovjednika,

1469
