1474
00:48:31,780 --> 00:48:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] nisam izvršio zadnju pokoru.

1475
00:48:33,800 --> 00:48:35,139
[SPEAKER_00] I ovaj mu kaže,

1476
00:48:35,139 --> 00:48:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] jedan od če je naš.

1477
00:48:42,840 --> 00:48:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, sada je snačno ljudima dao ideju.

1478
00:48:44,579 --> 00:48:48,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, ali gledajte,

1479
00:48:48,239 --> 00:48:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je anegdota.

1480
00:48:50,059 --> 00:48:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je znak,

1481
