[SPEAKER_00] stvari što se događa kod nekih ljudi,

1482
00:48:56,199 --> 00:48:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] što ja vidim u duhovnoj sceni,

1483
00:48:57,960 --> 00:48:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] u Zagrebu,

1484
00:48:58,519 --> 00:48:59,820
[SPEAKER_00] duhovna nezrelost.

1485
00:48:59,820 --> 00:49:02,780
[SPEAKER_00] Mjenjanje duhovnika,

1486
00:49:02,780 --> 00:49:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] mijenjanje ispovjednika,

1487
00:49:04,400 --> 00:49:06,659
[SPEAKER_00] i doslovce duhovni šoping.

1488
00:49:06,659 --> 00:49:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ideš ovdje za to,

1489
00:49:08,199 --> 00:49:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] aha, ja znam kakav je on.

1490
00:49:09,619 --> 00:49:12,719
[SPEAKER_00] I tako, ne, ne, drži se, jedno.

1491
00:49:13,559 --> 00:49:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] Drži se, jedno.

1492
00:49:14,519 --> 00:49:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] I to vrijedi za karizmu,

1493
00:49:16,840 --> 00:49:18,280
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno za duhovnost.

1494
00:49:18,280 --> 00:49:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu fala,

1495
00:49:20,199 --> 00:49:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] crkva je tako bogata.

1496
00:49:21,980 --> 00:49:24,860
[SPEAKER_00] Franjevačka,

1497
00:49:24,860 --> 00:49:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] Isusovačka,

1498
00:49:25,619 --> 00:49:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] Opus Dei,

1499
