[SPEAKER_00] pa ne o katekumeni,

1502
00:49:30,239 --> 00:49:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] ovo, ono, gledajte,

1503
00:49:31,119 --> 00:49:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi moji,

1504
00:49:31,579 --> 00:49:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] to je dano iz jednog razloga,

1505
00:49:34,340 --> 00:49:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] zato što Bog je velik.

1506
00:49:36,159 --> 00:49:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog zna da su njegova djeca različita.

1507
00:49:39,159 --> 00:49:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] Opredijelite se.

1508
00:49:42,840 --> 00:49:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da ste,

1509
00:49:43,539 --> 00:49:44,219
[SPEAKER_00] jeste opredijelite,

1510
00:49:44,219 --> 00:49:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] da ste tu i tako,

1511
00:49:45,119 --> 00:49:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala,

1512
