1565
00:51:20,579 --> 00:51:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek isti grijeh.

1566
00:51:21,739 --> 00:51:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ja uvijek kažem,

1567
00:51:22,440 --> 00:51:23,780
