1570
00:51:25,780 --> 00:51:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] I ona mi je kliker proradio,

1571
00:51:27,840 --> 00:51:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] ja kažem,

1572
00:51:28,139 --> 00:51:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] znaš,

1573
