1583
00:51:38,480 --> 00:51:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] to da mi nećete vjerao,

1584
00:51:39,739 --> 00:51:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] više ne grižim,

1585
00:51:40,380 --> 00:51:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali imam neki drugi grijeh sada.

1586
00:51:41,980 --> 00:51:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš,

1587
00:51:44,679 --> 00:51:45,139
[SPEAKER_00] ok,

1588
00:51:45,139 --> 00:51:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] gledajte,

1589
