1590
00:51:48,320 --> 00:51:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ok?

1591
00:51:49,579 --> 00:51:52,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ima razlog zašto Bog dopušta,

1592
00:51:52,860 --> 00:51:53,760
